<h1>Top 10 Fulfillment Companies in Ukraine 2026: Complete Comparison for International Sellers</h1>

<AuthorByline lang="en" datePublished="2026-04-09" readingTime="15" />

<aside class="blog-disclosure" role="note" aria-label="Authorship disclosure">
<strong>About this ranking:</strong> it was compiled by the MTP Group team &mdash; one of the 10 operators listed. We scored ourselves against the same 6 public criteria we used for competitors (see methodology below). Our self-score is flagged separately; we tried to be fair but cannot fully eliminate bias. For an objective decision, we recommend requesting quotes from 3&ndash;5 operators and comparing them directly.
</aside>

<p class="blog-lead">Ukraine's e-commerce fulfillment market is valued at an estimated $5&ndash;7 billion and growing 10&ndash;18% annually, even through active conflict. For international sellers, brands entering the Ukrainian market, or companies using Ukraine as a low-cost logistics hub for Eastern Europe, choosing a fulfillment partner is a strategic decision with significant financial implications. This guide evaluates 10 notable Ukrainian fulfillment operators against publicly verifiable criteria so you can narrow a shortlist faster.</p>

<p>We evaluated the 10 largest fulfillment operators in Ukraine against publicly verifiable criteria: warehouse capacity, per-shipment pricing (converted to USD at April 2026 rates, ~41 UAH/$1), integration ecosystem, war-resilience infrastructure, operational track record, and pricing transparency. Where an operator doesn't publish information, we mark it "N/A" rather than guessing. Your weighting may differ &mdash; the methodology below can be re-weighted for your business.</p>

<nav class="blog-toc">
